        Basic constructor. Calls implementation of EnergyNetworkAnalyzer.createFlowGraph(org.sopra.api.model.Graph<org.sopra.api.model.EnergyNode, org.sopra.api.model.PowerLine>, java.util.Optional<java.util.Map<org.sopra.api.model.producer.Producer, java.lang.Integer>>, java.util.Optional<java.util.Map<org.sopra.api.model.consumer.Consumer, java.lang.Integer>>) with constructor arguments producerCapacities, and consumerCapacities to initialize attribute flowGraph.

        The Map producerLevels, consumerLevels, and powerlineLevels are initialized with nodes of argument graph as keys and 0 values.
